# What is R?
Scripting language
Statistical programming language
4th most popular programming language (IEEE)
Large community #rstats
Advantages:
Open source
Lots of packages (libraries written by users)
Used by lots of statsy people...but then need to communicate stats to non-technical stakeholders, business analysts...

